        %h2 Bracket pre seeding
        %p
          The initial seeding is done by providing the Challonge Tournament Manager a player list sorted by skill:
          %br
          %div{style: 'margin-left: 20px;'}
            %i player_skill = points/participations + wins/(wins+losses)*100 + participations + self_assessment/5 + tournament_experience/10
          %br
          The final seeding is done manually by a TO or his/her representatives.

